{"tid":2063583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支爆】中國浙江油罐車爆炸 19死172傷200多間民宅受損","createTime":"2020-06-14T06:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T10:29:19.000Z","uid":293677,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ec20f7fa430727521981365abcdf37ed3c7e06","tid":2063583,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3197419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3197419&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=eb02c619\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3197419&h=ff354b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3197419</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-14 13:32:24<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國浙江省台州昨日發生油罐車爆炸意外，造成嚴重傷亡，截至14日10點為止，造成19死172傷，有超過200多間民宅受損。</span></span>至於爆炸威力為何如此強大，上海應用技術大學城市建設與安全工程學院副教授麻庭光指出，當時油罐車外洩的液態石油氣正好和空氣處於「最佳混和狀態」，因此造成劇烈爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3197145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3197145&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=b7575823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3197145&h=2dceea03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3197145</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/13/phplz516R.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F13%2Fphplz516R.jpg&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=29c0899f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F